{"tid":2320953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵一名查票員初步確診","createTime":"2020-12-11T07:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T12:32:04.000Z","uid":277339,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"692ae9ccf16e0a3b762201b39380351ab1c61029","tid":2320953,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:45:37.000Z","msg":"港鐵公司表示，一名負責顧客服務及收益保護人員，昨晚初步確診。他日常負責查票及顧客服務等工作，早前因為有親友初步確診，獲當局安排接受隔離檢疫。他並無病徵，最後當值日期為星期一，工作期間一直有佩戴口罩。 公司已即時清潔消毒他工作過的筲箕灣、北角及柴灣站後勤用地，以及位於天后站的辦公室，並會根據衞生防護中心的指引，追蹤密切接觸者。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2370281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2370281&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=f9d60d06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2370281</a>"},{"pid":"8127b9bff047286d434374c816bad7111f1817be","tid":2320953,"uid":216828,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:51:45.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abeff9b850600a822b5bc103e27c2b470535b5b","tid":2320953,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"4cc1ec0c49e58204ae1bb2f4cdd4dff5429c579c","tid":2320953,"uid":110043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"87b7810c9b503636dbaf43c793084f3788d9c3e2","tid":2320953,"uid":89382,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:54:43.000Z","msg":"抵撚死，下世小心d"},{"pid":"d8a5550fa4fe3b52e2063a3b9c72e0fc3474c31a","tid":2320953,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:54:55.000Z","msg":"查飛死全家"},{"pid":"4e8faea737f32cbeed6aa300b9b134c433bedf59","tid":2320953,"uid":230530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:55:06.000Z","msg":"景樂？"},{"pid":"0a50dac77c6d759b927c35b150ff7bb8b96753e8","tid":2